		<title>somiiux</title>
		<style>
			/* Fade-in dende negro ao entrar */
			body {
				opacity: 0;
				animation: fadeInFromBlack 1.2s ease forwards;
			}

			@keyframes fadeInFromBlack {
				from {
					background-color: #000;
					opacity: 0;
				}
				to {
					background-color: #0a0a0a;
					opacity: 1;
				}
			}

			body.locked {
				pointer-events: none;
			}

			.focus-in-somiiux {
				animation: focus-in-expand 1.2s
					cubic-bezier(0.25, 0.46, 0.45, 0.94) both;
			}

			@keyframes focus-in-expand {
				0% {
					filter: blur(14px);
					opacity: 0;
				}
				100% {
					filter: blur(0);
					opacity: 1;
				}
			}

			.focus-in-website {
				animation: focus-in-expand 1.2s
					cubic-bezier(0.25, 0.46, 0.45, 0.94) both;
			}

			@keyframes focus-in-expand {
				0% {
					filter: blur(14px);
					opacity: 0;
				}
				100% {
					filter: blur(0);
					opacity: 1;
				}
			}
		</style>
	</head>

	<body>
		<main id="mainContent" class="main-content">
			<h1 id="title" class="focus-in-somiiux">SOMIIUX</h1>
			<button id="biografiaBtn" class="biografia-btn">
				BIIO
			</button>
		</main>

		<section id="biografia" class="biografia-section">
			<div class="biografia-container">
				<h2 class="biografia-title">BIIO</h2>
				<div class="biografia-content">
					<p>
					SOMIIUX is an emergiing GROOVY AND HYPNOTIC DJ and producer based in galiicia.
					<br><br>
					Origiinally from O VALADOURO and living in A CORUÃ‘A, he discovered his passion for techno through the local scene, 
					attendiing clubs and events where he developed a deep connection with rhythm and the energy of electroniic music. 
					His style blends driiving grooves with hypnotic atmospheres, aiming to immerse the listener in a state of motiion and trance.
					<br><br>
					In 2022, together with his brother LUCASIITO, he purchased his first DJ controller and productiion software, marking 
					the begiinning of his creative journey. Since then, SOMIIUX has been shaping his sound, taking inspiiration from labels such as 
					HATE, VAULT SESSIONS or MUTUAL RYTM, as well as artiists like FUNK ASSAULT, HYDEN, LOBSTER, among others.
					<br><br>
					After a year and a half of exploratiion and learning, he began performing live â€” some sets alongside his brother and others 
					solo â€” experiiences that allowed him to connect directly with the audiience and bring his HYPNOTIC ENERGY to the dancefloor.
					He is currently in a continuous process of growth, refiniing both his music productiion in ableton and his djing techniique.
